  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 9
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## CP Map Operations\n\nMonitors the **CPMap** data structure \u2014 a strongly consistent, linearizable key-value store backed by Raft. All reads and writes go through the Raft leader for the group that owns the map.\n\n**Key questions this dashboard answers:**\n- How many entries are stored in each CP Map, and is that growing or shrinking over time? *(Entry Count)*\n- How much memory is each map consuming? Is any map approaching its `max-size-mb` limit? *(Storage)*\n- Are maps being created and destroyed at an unusual rate? *(Lifecycle)*\n- Which CP group is under the most write load? *(Per-group commit rate)*\n\n**Map-to-group assignment in this cluster:**\n| Maps | CP Group |\n|------|----------|\n| map0 \u2013 map4 | group1 |\n| map5 \u2013 map9 | group5 |\n\n**Filters:** **Cluster** selects the environment. **CP Group** restricts the Raft-level panels.\n\n**Normal state:** entry counts growing steadily as the traffic generator runs, storage well below 20 MB per map (`max-size-mb`), no unexpected destroyed maps."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Inventory Overview",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Live CP Maps",
      "description": "Active CPMap instances.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_cp_map_summary_live_count{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "live",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Destroyed CP Maps",
      "description": "Destroyed CPMap instances. A growing count indicates maps are being created and torn down \u2014 an anti-pattern for CP structures.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_cp_map_summary_destroyed_count{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "destroyed",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Entries (all maps)",
      "description": "Total number of entries summed across all CPMaps (uses max per map to avoid double-counting across members).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 10,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(max by (name) (hz_cp_map_size{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}))",
          "legendFormat": "entries",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
